Field Descriptions

FW_OV_WR_DATA

A write to this register will insert entropy back into the entropy source module flow. Both !!FW_OV_CONTROL.FW_OV_MODE and !!FW_OV_CONTROL.FW_OV_ENTROPY_INSERT bits need to be set to enable the insertion.
